Name: Meatfish Skewer Lv.2
Description: Recommend: Stormblade, Wind Knight, Heavy Guardian, Marksman, and Shield Knight.
Description$english: Recommend: Stormblade, Wind Knight, Heavy Guardian, Marksman, and Shield Knight.
Description2$english: Not only can you enjoy a large amount of fish and meat at the same time, but you can also hold it in your hand and eat it on the go, making it convenient and quick. It is said that the first sailor who tried it exclaimed "satisfied, satisfied!" after eating, which inspired the chef who invented the recipe to name it.

recipes.Name: Meatfish Skewer
recipes.Des:
Crafting yields products Lv.1, Lv.2, and Lv.3 at rates of 50%, 40%, and 10%, respectively.
Indulge in generous portions of fish and meat, crafted for easy, handheld enjoyment wherever you roam. Legend has it that the first sailor to taste this hearty creation was so overwhelmed with delight, he kept exclaiming "Yummy!"— a joyous moment that inspired the chef to name the dish in its honor.
